agent-log-viewer - Agent Log Viewer

USAGE:
    agent-log-viewer <log-file1> [log-file2]

DESCRIPTION:
    View agent log files in tmux session. Creates split panes for
    viewing multiple log files simultaneously.

ARGUMENTS:
    log-file1
        Primary log file to view (required)

    log-file2
        Secondary log file to view (optional)

EXAMPLES:
    agent-log-viewer /var/log/agent.log
    agent-log-viewer /var/log/agent.log /var/log/agent-error.log
